observability and monitoring.</p></li>
</ul>
<h3 local-id=3D"8bb0508c2186" id=3D"id-20260609LapuLapuETS,GOCCandObs-Patch=
ingandmaintenance">Patching and maintenance</h3>
<ul local-id=3D"bfee852e-8457-4235-8440-afd9adbb56f1">
<li local-id=3D"c20b4729-b1da-4729-9a80-fa458f49d09f">
<p local-id=3D"5430ee97154f">Implement weekday patching for non-gold and no=
n-batch applications and servers to reduce weekend workload, with Karen, Sr=
ikranth, and Kanu Rajesh leading the effort from the server team.</p></li>
</ul>
<h3 local-id=3D"d46f5d5c9c3c" id=3D"id-20260609LapuLapuETS,GOCCandObs-Incid=
entmanagement">Incident management</h3>
<ul local-id=3D"99c4d074-e113-42ed-991b-50044214275d">
<li local-id=3D"5821ad84-b658-4fa5-8388-c41a5d970591">
<p local-id=3D"0da42c348be7">Escalation of the server incident to the Red H=
at vendor for log analysis was discussed, and Jonan planned to follow up wi=
th Dennis for updates on the vendor's findings.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"913a8f38-013d-4dbf-a1f5-776360e60fbb">
<p local-id=3D"da164074a04c">The team resolved the server issue with a rest=
art, but the root cause of the server freezing remains under investigation =
by the vendor.</p></li>
</ul>
